QUESTION NO: 1
You are the Cisco Unified Communications Manager in Pass4sures.com.Your company
uses a centralized call processing model to connect their saw mills in Albany and
Columbus. Each mill is configured as a separate Location in Cisco Unified CallManager

many G.729 calls can be placed between Locations simultaneously?
A. 8
B. 9
C. 16
D. 10
Answer: D
